rently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Event/composedPath\"><code>Event.composedPath</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSlotElement\"><code>HTMLSlotElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>Node.getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Node/isConnected\"><code>Node.isConnected</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ShadowRoot\"><code>ShadowRoot</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\"><code>Window.customElements</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard obsolete\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Obsolete:</strong> This feature is obsolete. Although it may still work in some browsers, its use is discouraged since it could be removed at any time. Try to avoid using it.</p></div>\n\n<p>A interface <strong><code>HTMLShadowElement</code></strong> representa um elemento HTML <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, Ao qual é usado no <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Shadow DOM (en-US)</a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Esta interface herda as propriedades do <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Esta interface herda os métodos do <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a>.</em></p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"htmlshadowelement.getdistributednodes_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement/getDistributedNodes\"><code>HTMLShadowElement.getDistributedNodes()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Retorna uma estática <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a> do <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\">distributed nodes</a> associado com este elemento &lt;shadow&gt;.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Especificação</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comentário</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/webcomponents/spec/shadow/#the-shadow-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Shadow DOM<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'shadow' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsoleto</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLShadowElement","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/HTMLShadowElement/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Se Shadow DOM não é habilitado no Firefox, os elementos &lt;shadow&gt; se comportarão como <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Shadow DOM foi implementado primeiro no Firefox 28 e está por trás de uma preferência, <code>dom.webcomponents.enabled</code>, ao qual é desabilitado por padrão. [1]</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>O elemento HTML <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> , implementa esta interface.</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_shadow_DOM\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Shadow DOM (en-US)</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Propriedades","id":"propriedades"},{"text":"Métodos","id":"métodos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A interface HTMLShadowElement representa um elemento HTML <shadow> (en-US), Ao qual é usado no Shadow DOM (en-US).","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLShadowElement","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"HTMLShadowElement","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"HTMLShadowElement","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLShadowElement","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/htmlshadowelement","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/htmlshadowelement/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologi